name: Childrens Game: Fizzbuzz!
tagline: A program that is a direct copy of the childrens game "Fizzbuzz", made with Javascript.
body: Welcome to my Fizzbuzz page, this is a page to show how you can make the childrens game "Fizzbuzz" through a programming language called Javascript.
